  <ul>
    <li>The last Cabinet Decision was 26/7,<a href="#f3">3</a> when, after some discussion, Cabinet expressed the view that the US might desert Taiwan. In between these Cabinet decisions, matters have been decided by the Prime Minister.</li>
  </ul>
</blockquote>

